description: Quality Online Education Group Inc., an e-learning company, provides online English lessons to students in China. The company offers online English programs for pre-school to grades 6, white label online tutoring services, and end-to-end management software solutions for education institutions. It also provides professional recruitment services for education organizations seeking educators. The company was formerly known as ADGS Advisory, Inc. and changed its name to Quality Online Education Group Inc. in May 2021. Quality Online Education Group Inc. is based in Richmond Hill, Canada.
